    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 engineering. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six benefits from a recently calibrated VANOS unit and comprehensive valve adjustment, ensuring the individual throttle bodies deliver linear power delivery throughout the rev range. Power is transmitted via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior displays honest patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains tight and responsive. A performance-oriented specimen optimized for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
