    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver, offering a perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014typical of careful highway commuting. The alloy wheels are curb-rash free and wrapped in high-quality tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather seating is supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, supported by a complete folder of service records. It recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and received a fresh synthetic oil change and new cabin air filters. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. This is a turn-key vehicle for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been treated with consistent care and respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
